{"tid":1379711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[驅散犬類] 效法沙田 天水圍朋友","createTime":"2019-07-28T23:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T01:37:42.000Z","uid":264079,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81f00c8fb916255b798e3b10c534904cb0230e2d","tid":1379711,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:55:10.000Z","msg":"住新界西嘅朋友，居住地方偏遠，經常有犬隻徘徊，阻小朋友返屋企，大家可以學吓沙田，天水圍盟友<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrWFszz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrWFszz.png&h=1e3f6f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9zomHNXb_PE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9zomHNXb_PE&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=9078527d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9zomHNXb_PE</a><br />\n<br />\n天水圍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/395070774470142?s=633603805&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fvideos%2F395070774470142%3Fs%3D633603805%26sfns%3Dmo&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=50862d80\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/395070774470142?s=633603805&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬧走啲狗</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">低成本，高效益</span></span><br />\n如有師奶，效果更佳<br />\n<br />\n細路好慘，做得幾多得幾多"},{"pid":"c08d1092d801ae482439de4832665abedbf695fe","tid":1379711,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:06:59.000Z","msg":"今日3pm港澳辦開記招 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日一定好多水軍洗版帶風向想分化各位手足</span></span> <br />\n大家緊記宗旨唔好被輕易帶動! <br />\n邊個話袋住先就屌鳩佢老母<br />\n<br />\n死左咁多、拉左咁多義士要我地算數？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路走來咁辛苦唔好輕易